<item>
            <title>[FLINK-2194] Type extractor does not support Writable type</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2194</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The type extractor supports sub types of &lt;tt&gt;Writable&lt;/tt&gt; but not &lt;tt&gt;Writable&lt;/tt&gt; itself. The reason is that it wants to create a &lt;tt&gt;WritableTypeInfo&lt;/tt&gt; which is not possible for the interface &lt;tt&gt;Writable&lt;/tt&gt;, though. A solution would be to treat the &lt;tt&gt;Writable&lt;/tt&gt; interface like a generic type. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
