                            <comment id="14580172" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2015 07:41:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user tillrohrmann opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/814&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/814&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2194&quot; title=&quot;Type extractor does not support Writable type&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-2194&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-2194&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;type extractor&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Treats Writable type as generic type (interface)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Adds check so that the `Writable` type is treated as a generic type.&lt;/p&gt;

