&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2194&quot; title=&quot;Type extractor does not support Writable type&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-2194&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-2194&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;type extractor&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Excludes Writable type from WritableTypeInformation to be treated as an interface&lt;/p&gt;

